seller.oneLinerTitle: I LOVE TO DO MODERN AND PROFESSIONAL LOGO
seller.description: I am Thomas Jacky. I am a freelancer. Professionally I am a graphics designer. I have over 7 years experience in this sector. At first in my job career was an employer in a printing firm. Now I am self-dependable! Give me your job without hesitation because this is my profession.

reviews.comment: Seller reached out to me almost immediately after placing my gig requesting a different format of our logo. Delivered revised logos to me very quickly. Satisfied with initial order so no revisions required. I forgot that the gig is automatically accepted/closed after 3 days so being I had a 3 day weekend, I missed viewing the gig before acceptance. But because the Seller delivered great logos initially it didn't matter because I didn't want revisions.

Satisfactory overall, the seller is very fast and did everything as asked. I was hoping that he can expand from some abstract instruction, however in the end I had to think and do my own exploration and sketch on how the logo should exactly look like. Again, the seller did everything as asked, but the instructions can't be abstract.
Jacky is responsive and timely and his work is fine. I think my project had too many nuances that cannot be correctly understood under the current model of Fiverr. I got what I paid for.

My artist was great, and he was fast with turnaround times. The process was very simple, intuitive and easy to follow. Additionally the price was great! I will be using Fiverr in the future and happy to refer others as well.
I gave them a logo that had horrible choppy thin lines and they absolutely made it look perfect! I didn’t think it was possible! Very fast delivery!
